Laboratory experiment designed to study the Sun-like line-tied MFRs (Myers et al. 2015)










Potential field decay index n


n(z) = - \frac{z}{|\mathbf{B}_\text{pot}|}\frac{\partial |\mathbf{B}_\text{pot}|}{\partial z}


Edge safety factor q_a : inverse of the edge magnetic twist \iota_a


q_a = \frac{2\pi}{\iota_a} = \left.\frac{\rm{d}\Phi_\text{T}}{\rm{d}\psi_\text{P}}\right|_{r=a} \approx \frac{2\pi a}{L}\frac{B_\text{Ta}}{B_\text{Pa}}

